snippet.textDisplay:
الا بذكرالله تطمءن القلوب.
Verily the remembrance of God pacifies the hearts.

Peace and love for all from the religion preached by the man who was رحمت لالعالمين. Peace and mercy to the world. Islam is an Abrahamic religion and hence these names are the way we know Moses's Yahweh and Jesus's God.
